2","tid":1678762,"uid":134974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7a85fed721a7bf29b44fae3b16c30685fcebe51","tid":1678762,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a62e4cdfb4417b40a8b5a9a100e720b325d0d200","tid":1678762,"uid":278659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:15:34.000Z","msg":"師兄 如果我咁做正確嗎<br />\n<br />\ndim price as string <br />\n<br />\nPrice = inputbox(&ldquo;enter a price&rdquo;) <br />\n <br />\nPrice = CDbl(price)<br />\n<br />\nMsgbox  price"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"唔係太熟, 不過盡量避免用同一個字declare variables?<br />\n<br />\n試下用VarType(varname) 黎check下個variable type<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/office/vba/language/reference/user-interface-help/vartype-function\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Foffice%2Fvba%2Flanguage%2Freference%2Fuser-interface-help%2Fvartype-function&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4RYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=ad030aa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/office/vba/language/reference/user-interface-help/vartype-function</a><br />\n5: Double<br />\n8: String<br />\n<br />\n同埋, 你第二句好似調轉左?<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">dim price_str as string , Price_dou as Double\nprice_str= inputbox(&ldquo;enter a price&rdquo;) \nPrice_dou= CDbl(price_str)\nMsgbox VarType(Price_dou)\nMsgbox VarType(price_str) </code></pre>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T21:59:56.000Z","msg":"直接<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">dim Price as Double\nPrice = CDbl(inputbox(&ldquo;enter a price&rdquo;))\nMsgbox VarType(Price)</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:10:24.000Z","msg":"如果已經dim左 double 仲要再用CDbl 去轉double 嗎？ 不過我最後唔知點解<br />\nDim price as variant <br />\n<br />\nPrice = inputbox(enter a price)<br />\n<br />\nTotal = price * quantity <br />\n<br />\nMsgbox total<br />\n<br />\n係做到calculation <br />\n我以為一旦輸入price <br />\n之後price 就會變左 string 比如（&lsquo;&rsquo;10.99&lsquo;&rsquo;） 導致做唔到calculation"},{"pid":"11b7c4ee62e6d1bdc779bda33054a8ab09c17088","tid":1678762,"uid":278659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7a85fed721a7bf29b44fae3b16c30685fcebe51","tid":1678762,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a62e4cdfb4417b40a8b5a9a100e720b325d0d200","tid":1678762,"uid":278659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afe2e27fa74639ce437dfe3dbdd79c4a23815427","tid":1678762,"uid":108674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:03:05.000Z","msg":"input box 必須係string<br />\n<br />\ndim xxx as string<br />\n之後operation再轉返做double"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:15:34.000Z","msg":"師兄 如果我咁做正確嗎<br />\n<br />\ndim price as string <br />\n<br />\nPrice = inputbox(&ldquo;enter a price&rdquo;) <br />\n <br />\nPrice = CDbl(price)<br />\n<br />\nMsgbox  price"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"唔係太熟, 不過盡量避免用同一個字declare variables?<br />\n<br />\n試下用VarType(varname) 黎check下個variable type<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/office/vba/language/reference/user-interface-help/vartype-function\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Foffice%2Fvba%2Flanguage%2Freference%2Fuser-interface-help%2Fvartype-function&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4RYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=ad030aa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/office/vba/language/reference/user-interface-help/vartype-function</a><br />\n5: Double<br />\n8: String<br />\n<br />\n同埋, 你第二句好似調轉左?<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">dim price_str as string , Price_dou as Double\nprice_str= inputbox(&ldquo;enter a price&rdquo;) \nPrice_dou= CDbl(price_str)\nMsgbox VarType(Price_dou)\nMsgbox VarType(price_str) </code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"原來有function 可以check vartype 㗎！<br />\n學到野 多謝曬！<br />\n<br />\n我最後用你上邊條code都係唔知點解出現overflow<br />\n<br />\n所以用dim price as variant 解決左⋯"}]}